= wfo - wiki frontend at offline

== Author

Tanaka Akira <akr@fsij.org>

== License

GPL

== Feature

* checkout a wiki page as a local file
* edit the file
* update the file
* commit the file to the wiki
* supported wiki and blog systems:
  * qwikWeb
  * Trac's wiki
  * tDiary

== Requirements

* ruby-1.8.3
* htree-0.4

== Download

  % svn co svn://svn@rx1620.fsij.org/akr/wvs/trunk wvs

== Install

  % ./configure
  % make
  % make install

configure option:

  --prefix=PREFIX         install architecture-independent files in PREFIX
  --with-ruby=PATHNAME    use ruby interpreter specified by PATHNAME

== Usage

  wvs checkout [-t repo_type] URL [local-filename][.ext]
  wvs status [-u] [local-filename...]
  wvs update [local-filename...]
  wvs commit [local-filename...]
  wvs diff [-u] [local-filename...]
  wvs workdump [local-filename...]

== Authentication

  % mkdir ~/.keyring
  % cd ~/.keyring

  * TypeKey
    % echo typekey-username typekey-password | gpg --comment TypeKey -e -a --default-recipient-self > typekey.asc

